RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: GWTM_AMEND_MASTER.EXT_SYSTEM = GWTM_AMEND_NODES.EXT_SYSTEM AND GWTM_AMEND_MASTER.SOURCE_OPERATION = GWTM_AMEND_NODES.SOURCE_OPERATION AND GWTM_AMEND_MASTER.ORIGIN_SYSTEM = GWTM_AMEND_NODES.ORIGIN_SYSTEM

GWTM_AMEND_NODES.EXT_SYSTEM = GWTM_AMEND_FIELDS.EXT_SYSTEM AND GWTM_AMEND_NODES.SOURCE_OPERATION = GWTM_AMEND_FIELDS.SOURCE_OPERATION AND GWTM_AMEND_NODES.NODE_NAME = GWTM_AMEND_FIELDS.NODE_NAME AND GWTM_AMEND_NODES.ORIGIN_SYSTEM = GWTM_AMEND_FIELDS.ORIGIN_SYSTEM

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT EXT_SYSTEM FROM GWTM_EXT_SYS_MASTER WHERE ONCE_AUTH = 'Y' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' ORDER BY EXT_SYSTEM
SELECT service_name from (SELECT DISTINCT(SERVICE_NAME) FROM gwtb_amend_nodes union SELECT DISTINCT(SERVICE_NAME) FROM gwtb_amend_fields) WHERE 1=1 ORDER BY SERVICE_NAME

select operation_code, fc_function_id, fc_action from gwtm_operations_master where (service_name, operation_code) IN (select service_name, operation_code from(SELECT service_name, operation_code FROM gwtb_amend_nodes g where g.service_name = ? union SELECT service_name, operation_code FROM gwtb_amend_fields h where h.service_name = ?)) ORDER BY operation_code
SELECT DISTINCT (SOURCE_OPERATION) FROM GWTM_AMEND_NODES ORDER BY SOURCE_OPERATION

SELECT Node_Name FROM (SELECT DISTINCT Node_Name FROM Gwtb_Amend_Nodes WHERE Service_Name = ? AND Operation_Code = ? UNION SELECT DISTINCT Node_Name FROM Gwtb_Amend_Fields WHERE Service_Name = ? AND Operation_Code = ? UNION SELECT DISTINCT Node_Name FROM Gwtb_Amend_Nodes WHERE (Service_Name, Operation_Code) IN (SELECT Call_Form, Call_Form || '_' || Action FROM (SELECT c.Call_Form, CASE WHEN EXISTS (SELECT a.Fc_Action FROM Gwtm_Operations_Master a, Smtb_Menu b WHERE Service_Name = ? AND Operation_Code = ? AND a.Fc_Function_Id = b.Function_Id) THEN (SELECT CASE WHEN a.Fc_Action = 'MODIFY' AND b.Routing_Type <> 'X' THEN 'AMEND' ELSE a.Fc_Action END AS Action FROM Gwtm_Operations_Master a, Smtb_Menu b WHERE Service_Name = ? AND Operation_Code = ? AND a.Fc_Function_Id = b.Function_Id) ELSE (SELECT CASE WHEN a.Routing_Type = 'X' AND Substr(?, Instr(?, '_', -1) + 1) = 'AMEND' THEN 'MODIFY' ELSE Substr(?, Instr(?, '_', -1) + 1) END AS Action FROM Smtb_Menu a WHERE Function_Id = c.Call_Form) END AS Action FROM Cstb_Fid_Callforms c WHERE Function_Id IN (SELECT Fc_Function_Id FROM Gwtm_Operations_Master WHERE Service_Name = ? AND Operation_Code = ? UNION SELECT Service_Name FROM Gwtb_Amend_Nodes WHERE Service_Name = ? AND Operation_Code = ?))))WHERE 1 = 1

select distinct field_name from (select * from GWTB_AMEND_FIELDS WHERE SERVICE_NAME = ? AND OPERATION_CODE = ? AND NODE_NAME = ? UNION SELECT * FROM GWTB_AMEND_FIELDS WHERE NODE_NAME = ? AND (SERVICE_NAME,OPERATION_CODE) IN ( SELECT Call_Form, Call_Form || '_' || Action FROM (SELECT c.Call_Form, CASE WHEN EXISTS (SELECT a.Fc_Action FROM Gwtm_Operations_Master a, Smtb_Menu b WHERE Service_Name = ? AND Operation_Code = ? AND a.Fc_Function_Id = b.Function_Id) THEN (SELECT CASE WHEN a.Fc_Action = 'MODIFY' AND b.Routing_Type <> 'X' THEN 'AMEND' ELSE a.Fc_Action END AS Action FROM Gwtm_Operations_Master a, Smtb_Menu b WHERE Service_Name = ? AND Operation_Code = ? AND a.Fc_Function_Id = b.Function_Id) ELSE (SELECT CASE WHEN a.Routing_Type = 'X' AND Substr(?, Instr(?, '_', -1) + 1) = 'AMEND' THEN 'MODIFY' ELSE Substr(?, Instr(?, '_', -1) + 1) END AS Action FROM Smtb_Menu a WHERE Function_Id = c.Call_Form) END AS Action FROM Cstb_Fid_Callforms c WHERE Function_Id IN (SELECT Fc_Function_Id FROM Gwtm_Operations_Master WHERE Service_Name = ? AND Operation_Code = ? UNION SELECT Service_Name FROM Gwtb_Amend_Nodes WHERE Service_Name = ? AND Operation_Code = ?))))
SELECT EXT_SYSTEM FROM GWTM_EXT_SYS_MASTER WHERE ONCE_AUTH = 'Y' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' ORDER BY EXT_SYSTEM
